# Normalize line endings to LF in the repository across agent/contributor
# platforms; check out with the platform's native convention. Keeps diffs
# free of CRLF churn. Binary files are auto-detected and left untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf

# uv.lock is intentionally NOT marked linguist-generated: its diffs are part
# of dependency review and must stay visible in pull requests.
